{
  "name": "trade-missed-payment",
  "description": "Same treaty setup as trade-flow but Guatemala starts with wealthStock=5 (just enough to cover 5 Wealth collateral). After collateral is deducted Guatemala has 0 Wealth. The trade clause demands 6 Wealth/tick — exceeding Guatemala's 5/tick production. Trade evaluation runs before production each tick, so Guatemala misses payment at T1 (0 < 6) and T2 (5 < 6), hitting the consecutive-miss breach threshold of 2. Expected: missed_payment events at T1 and T2, clause breaches at T2, Guatemala Trust −20, collateral transferred to Costa Rica.",
